Installation:

- Create a mySQL database and execute as mysql admin:

  mysql> CREATE DATABASE phtagr;
  mysql> GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON phtagr.* TO 'phtagr'@'localhost' \
      IDENTIFIED BY '<PASSWD>'; 

- Checkout the newest branch from svn to a webbrowser directory like
  ~/.public_html or /var/www

  $ svn co http://svn.inspirationslos.de/phtagr/trunk/phtagr

- Open the index.php with your webbrowser and follow the installation
  instructions.
